      "text": "MAJOR WIN for international law enforcement!\n\nU.S. and Panamanian authorities just secured the extradition of Reza Dindar—wanted for conspiring to illegally export sensitive U.S. technology to Iran.\n\nThis operation brought together the Diplomatic Security Service along with our federal partners from HSI, CBP, DEA, USMS, and Commerce's BIS in a textbook example of interagency teamwork.\n\nThe message is clear: We will pursue those who threaten our national security—no matter where they hide.\n\nLaw enforcement partnerships work. Our technology stays protected. Justice prevails. Tags: @DHSgov , @CBP , @DEAHQ  , @BISgov , @ICEgov , @USMarshalsHQ",
